These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-1::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  analyst, firefighter, nurse, pilot, security-guard, social-worker
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: rose, tulip, daisy, lily, orchid, balloon-flower
1. the pilot is on the left of the nurse##1
2. the person who growstulip is on the left of the social-worker##1
3. the analyst is on the left of the firefighter##1
4. the person who growsorchid is between the social-worker and the person who growsrose##2
5. the person who growslily is between the person who growsorchid and the person who growstulip##2
6. the person who growsrose is the pilot##1
7. the security-guard is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
8. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the firefighter##1
9. the security-guard is on the right of the social-worker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |       3       |       4        |    5     |   6    |
| Job           | analyst | firefighter | social-worker | security-guard | pilot    | nurse  |
| Flower   | balloon-flower | tulip   | lily       | orchid        | rose | daisy |

