.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: begonia, balloon-flower, poppy, aconite, rose, zinnia
6 different pets are kept: frog, goat, guinea-pig, horse, lizard, snake
1. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
3. the owner of the horse is between the person who growsaconite and the person who growsbegonia##2
4. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
5. the person who growsbegonia is on the far right##1
6. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
7. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
8. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| Flower   | balloon-flower | zinnia | rose | aconite | poppy | begonia  |
| Pet           | snake | lizard  | frog | goat    | horse  | guinea-pig |

