.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: epic, zombie, western, fantasy, horror, superhero
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, roller, scooter, taxi, trike
1. the person driving the roller is the person watching fantasy movies##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
4. the person driving the scooter is the person watching zombie movies##1
5. the person watching epic movies is the person driving the bike##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the bike and the person watching superhero movies##2
7. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
8. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |   6    |
| Movie-Genre        | zombie    | superhero | western | epic | horror | fantasy   |
| Transport   | scooter | taxi        | quad-bike  | bike     | trike  | roller |

