.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-6::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: thriller, drama, spy, comedy, animation, sports
The people have 6 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, dancing, reading, traveling, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
5. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
6. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
7. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person watching sports movies##1
8. the person watching spy movies is between the person watching comedy movies and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
9. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| Movie-Genre    | thriller | sports | animation  | comedy      | spy | drama  |
| Hobby   | card-games  | dancing    | reading | board-games | traveling | woodworking |

