.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-8::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: tram, trike, car, bus, roller, jet-ski
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: blues, disco, gospel, indie, jazz, trance
1. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of disco##1
3. the fan of trance is between the fan of jazz and the fan of blues##2
4. the person driving the bus is the fan of gospel##1
5. the person driving the car is between the person driving the trike and the person driving the roller##2
6. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of trance##1
7. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
8. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
9. the person driving the car is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Transport           | bus | jet-ski | roller | car | trike | tram |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | indie   | disco         | blues    | trance     | jazz     |

