The people prefer 6 different types of sport: biathlon, sailing, skateboarding, skiing, soccer, surfing
 1. the person watching western movies is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person watching superhero movies and the person who's sport is surfing##2
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's sport is skiing is the person watching western movies##1
 5. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is the person watching western movies##1
 7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 8. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 9. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
10. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1

