4. the person watching comedy movies is the ranch-style house##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is between the person watching family movies and the person watching documentary movies##2
6. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
7. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the modern house##1
