.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-11::.
6 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, frog, hedgehog, rabbit, snake
There are 6 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, fanta, water, sprite, iced-tea, hot-chocolate
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 2. the owner of the rabbit is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking fanta and the owner of the frog##2
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 9. the owner of the cat is between the person drinking soy-milk and the owner of the chinchilla##2
10. the owner of the hedgehog is the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |
| Pet         | snake   | rabbit | frog       | hedgehog | cat    | chinchilla |
| Beverage   | fanta | iced-tea  | water | soy-milk      | sprite | hot-chocolate        |

