.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-14::.
There 6 different types of food: avocado, banana, mango, onion, peas, zucchini
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: april, december, september, july, march, august
 1. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating peas##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person eating banana##2
 3. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person eating zucchini and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
 5. the person eating zucchini is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person eating mango##2
 6. the person eating onion is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 7. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person eating banana##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 9. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
10. the person eating onion is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4     |       5        |      6       |
| Food   | onion     | avocado | peas   | mango     | zucchini       | banana       |
| Birthday    | december | july   | april | march | august | september |

