 4. the montecristo-smoker is on the far right##1
 5. the aristoff-smoker is the german##1
 6. the prince-smoker is the malaysian##1
 7. the dunhill-smoker is the dunhill-smoker##1
 8. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 9. the indonesian is on the left of the polish##1
10. the indonesian is on the right of the prince-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |   5    |     6     |
| Cigar   | game | aristoff    | prince     | vegafina      | dunhill    | montecristo |
| Nationality   | indian | german | malaysian | indonesian | polish | japanese  |

