3. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person playing snooker##2
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
7. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
8. the person playing go is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1

