.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-17::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: country, d&b, jazz, metal, punk, rock
There are 6 different favourite colors: blood-red, fuchsia, ebony, red, lavender, amber
1. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the fan of punk##1
2. the person who likes blood-red is the fan of metal##1
3. the fan of country is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes lavender is the fan of country##1
5. the fan of rock is between the fan of jazz and the fan of d&b##2
6. the fan of metal is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
7. the fan of d&b is on the far right##1
8. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
9. the person who likes red is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |       5       |   6    |
| Music-Genre   | country | metal      | punk       | jazz    | rock          | d&b    |
| Color         | lavender  | blood-red | amber | fuchsia | ebony | red |

